{"id": "ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 445, "displayName": {"text": "Miller & Lux Restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Upscale destination with an old-school vibe offering steak & Caesar salad, plus wine & cocktails.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xndFNHdzRTamhRVUZjdFNsRjJSREV3VlZWT1gyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Dinner at Miller & Lux with coworkers was an outstanding experience from start to finish. We started with several appetizers including the Beets & Goat Cheese Salad, Beef Noodle Soup, Wagyu Meatballs with Mezze Rigatoni, and the Poached Shrimp Cocktail with Fresno chili cocktail sauce — every dish was flavorful, fresh, and generously portioned.\n\nFor the main courses, we shared the Roasted Duroc Pork Tomahawk, which was incredibly tender and packed with flavor, the French Dover Sole Meunière finished tableside, and the Pan-Seared Hokkaido Scallops with pomme purée, peas, and petite carrots. We also ordered sides of lobster pesto risotto, asparagus, and Yukon Gold purée potatoes, all of which were delicious and perfect for sharing.\n\nTo finish the evening, we enjoyed espresso, cappuccino, a huge banana split, and the lemon blueberry tart — the perfect ending to a fantastic meal.\n\nThe service was excellent, attentive, and very detailed in explaining each dish. Overall, a great dining experience with amazing food, generous portions, and top-notch hospitality. We’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Dinner at Miller & Lux with coworkers was an outstanding experience from start to finish. We started with several appetizers including the Beets & Goat Cheese Salad, Beef Noodle Soup, Wagyu Meatballs with Mezze Rigatoni, and the Poached Shrimp Cocktail with Fresno chili cocktail sauce — every dish was flavorful, fresh, and generously portioned.\n\nFor the main courses, we shared the Roasted Duroc Pork Tomahawk, which was incredibly tender and packed with flavor, the French Dover Sole Meunière finished tableside, and the Pan-Seared Hokkaido Scallops with pomme purée, peas, and petite carrots. We also ordered sides of lobster pesto risotto, asparagus, and Yukon Gold purée potatoes, all of which were delicious and perfect for sharing.\n\nTo finish the evening, we enjoyed espresso, cappuccino, a huge banana split, and the lemon blueberry tart — the perfect ending to a fantastic meal.\n\nThe service was excellent, attentive, and very detailed in explaining each dish. Overall, a great dining experience with amazing food, generous portions, and top-notch hospitality. We’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Giuseppe Cascio", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105565460674815429295/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6lpArvdJRj9VDWqo9ONiUzx5a_2xslSTDb1WlAslR9Ut6Fao=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T05:16:33.293816432Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xndFNHdzRTamhRVUZjdFNsRjJSREV3VlZWT1gyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xndFNHdzRTamhRVUZjdFNsRjJSREV3VlZWT1gyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f51e71f14f5:0x6eafa312fb44a44"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMVRHZEJka2MxV1RrdGRWaHJiV2RKWldKc1ZsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We had dinner here to celebrate my husband’s birthday. The service is impeccable. The food was great! Best Cesar salad I have EVER had especially if you like anchovies (optional). They make it at your table! My daughter enjoyed the fluffy butter and bread as well as the heap of black truffle Parmesan fries. We had the NY steak, ribeye, potato puree, truffle mac n cheese, and a choice of sauce on the side for the steaks. The dessert menu was tempting; however we were so stuffed!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We had dinner here to celebrate my husband’s birthday. The service is impeccable. The food was great! Best Cesar salad I have EVER had especially if you like anchovies (optional). They make it at your table! My daughter enjoyed the fluffy butter and bread as well as the heap of black truffle Parmesan fries. We had the NY steak, ribeye, potato puree, truffle mac n cheese, and a choice of sauce on the side for the steaks. The dessert menu was tempting; however we were so stuffed!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michelle Victorio Perez-Licaros", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106300338923514393592/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbswMrFr-tMU_Ak7zNaY_G---AQpLSUl-r6FUutU3pHuNYIFFk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T02:21:13.570629605Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMVRHZEJka2MxV1RrdGRWaHJiV2RKWldKc1ZsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kMVRHZEJka2MxV1RrdGRWaHJiV2RKWldKc1ZsRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f51e71f14f5:0x6eafa312fb44a44"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psR2N6Sk9WbXhwUmpObmVGbGxaVXRYZFdsdE0wRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I came here to celebrate my lovers’ birthday and we had the creamed kale, beat salad, Australian Wagyu Tomahawk, truffle mac and cheese and the chocolate chip cookie with vanilla ice cream. The food was good, the service however was very good. All the employees were very attentive and our waitress was knowledgeable and did an excellent job. The food lacked a little bit of flavor and I wasn’t impressed but overall great experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came here to celebrate my lovers’ birthday and we had the creamed kale, beat salad, Australian Wagyu Tomahawk, truffle mac and cheese and the chocolate chip cookie with vanilla ice cream. The food was good, the service however was very good. All the employees were very attentive and our waitress was knowledgeable and did an excellent job. The food lacked a little bit of flavor and I wasn’t impressed but overall great experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Evelyn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104320118201538828970/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrlTelyNVdptahT2cLRQjvXk8AuPmHUpt1p0m2IrVGc2c-6A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T07:19:16.907132251Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psR2N6Sk9WbXhwUmpObmVGbGxaVXRYZFdsdE0wRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psR2N6Sk9WbXhwUmpObmVGbGxaVXRYZFdsdE0wRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f51e71f14f5:0x6eafa312fb44a44"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvMFNHOXplVGx5TFcxeFJHbE9NSFZ1YUVzMGVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Came here for dinner before a show at the chase arena… very pretty. Everyone greets you and welcomes you in. Staff were very attentive. We ordered some appetizers and the table side Caesar salad which was delicious. My husband ordered the filet and I ordered the chicken dish. His steak came out cold. Ice cold. We sent it back and they brought back a new one pretty quickly which he enjoyed. Our side dishes that we ordered also came out wrong, but again were corrected quickly. At the end of the dinner he ordered a to go chocolate cake to be added to our food that we had packed up to go… when we swung by after the show to pick up our food (which is nice they offered to hold it for us) the chocolate cake was NOT in our to go bag. At that point they had already closed so we didn’t even bother asking about it. Overall the experience was fine, just not Michelin star level which we saw it was on the Michelin guide… eh. lol maybe we will try again?", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here for dinner before a show at the chase arena… very pretty. Everyone greets you and welcomes you in. Staff were very attentive. We ordered some appetizers and the table side Caesar salad which was delicious. My husband ordered the filet and I ordered the chicken dish. His steak came out cold. Ice cold. We sent it back and they brought back a new one pretty quickly which he enjoyed. Our side dishes that we ordered also came out wrong, but again were corrected quickly. At the end of the dinner he ordered a to go chocolate cake to be added to our food that we had packed up to go… when we swung by after the show to pick up our food (which is nice they offered to hold it for us) the chocolate cake was NOT in our to go bag. At that point they had already closed so we didn’t even bother asking about it. Overall the experience was fine, just not Michelin star level which we saw it was on the Michelin guide… eh. lol maybe we will try again?", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michelle M", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115899312166220822029/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3aFz1X3DaY594GUcZQ1e4jbDRM8V0rVApQuWihyMpTbpY5Pw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-09T19:36:55.347413073Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvMFNHOXplVGx5TFcxeFJHbE9NSFZ1YUVzMGVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvMFNHOXplVGx5TFcxeFJHbE9NSFZ1YUVzMGVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f51e71f14f5:0x6eafa312fb44a44"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0LzH66gY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRlVqRlNiV2s0T1RSWGJqVnNTak0xZEdWZlQxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Food: 3/5\nService: 4/5\nAmbiance: 4/5\nPortion to Price: 2/5\nOverall: A standard fare steak joint.\n\nThe extended review...\n\nFood: 3/5 - We tried the canapes, the Caesar salad, and shared few of the steaks.  All the tastes were pretty standard fare.\n\nService: 4/5 - Friendly and attentive services.\n\nAmbiance: 4/5 - Quite a nice setting with a of comfortable seating\n\nPortion to Price: 2/5 - Price was a bit on the pricier side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Food: 3/5\nService: 4/5\nAmbiance: 4/5\nPortion to Price: 2/5\nOverall: A standard fare steak joint.\n\nThe extended review...\n\nFood: 3/5 - We tried the canapes, the Caesar salad, and shared few of the steaks.  All the tastes were pretty standard fare.\n\nService: 4/5 - Friendly and attentive services.\n\nAmbiance: 4/5 - Quite a nice setting with a of comfortable seating\n\nPortion to Price: 2/5 - Price was a bit on the pricier side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Spencer Q", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117102971375246814482/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXkFjYC31DkN6yWs542Nxx90Ya93wm1u5ieqe6m1I3rAtnePdz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-30T17:47:00.442574663Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRlVqRlNiV2s0T1RSWGJqVnNTak0xZEdWZlQxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRlVqRlNiV2s0T1RSWGJqVnNTak0xZEdWZlQxRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7f51e71f14f5:0x6eafa312fb44a44"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ9RQf51F_j4ARREq0